      • isAcknowledged

        public boolean isAcknowledged()
        Returns true if the creation of the new rollover index and switching of the alias to the newly created index was successful, and returns false otherwise. If isDryRun() is true, then this will also return false. If this returns false, then isShardsAcked() will also return false.

      • isShardsAcked

        public boolean isShardsAcked()
        Returns true if the requisite number of shards were started in the newly created rollover index before returning. If isAcknowledged() is false, then this will also return false.
